case.title: Yummy mummy seeks... - 31
case.text:
...a yummy man for dating.
I'd love it if you are tall, dark and handsome but we don't always get what we want in life so I'd prefer if you were sane and stable with good hygiene.
I am a pretty, dark skinned girl who's witty and sweet with my own strong opinions and a naughty streak. x
